name: Glitch v002 - 7h12d 3y3
description:
The second piece of recovered data in the animated Glitch series. 

Glitch Series - A recent solar flare hit the Space Lab and completely corrupted a harddrive of data... Space Lab's proprietary AI technology, EVA, was able to utilize its Neural Framework Technology to salvage several pieces - although they are badly damaged. This is a series of the recovered data.
